			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This AD plays during the Ketheric Showdown in the lower Colony. It will play on Ketheric if Isobel is killed during the combat.\r\n\r\n- Load SCL_Main_A\r\n- Using ReCon command \"oe KethericShowdown_Start\"  to teleport yourself there.\r\n- Use command \"oe KethericShowdown_AudienceRoute\" to make sure Isobel is here, and tadpoled.\r\n- Go through the dialog, approach Ketheric, go through that dialog too. Combat will start.\r\n- To check the Apostle form version, use \"oe KethericShowdown_Transform\".\r\n- Kill Isobel (either through ReCon or in-game combat). This AD will play on Ketheric."
				},
